# VibeCraft — Fighter 3-D Model (Wavefront OBJ)
#
# Low-poly humanoid warrior wielding a sword (right hand) and a
# kite shield (left arm).  Designed to read cleanly in plain text,
# diff well in Git, and render as a recognisable silhouette at any
# camera distance.
#
# Dimensions  : ~2.0 units tall, centred at origin
# Poly count  : 78 triangles
# Convention  : Y-up, right-handed coordinate system
#
# Parts:
#   Head        — bevelled cube (helmet with visor slit)
#   Torso       — tapered box with pauldrons (shoulder guards)
#   Waist       — belt section
#   Left Arm    — upper arm + forearm + kite shield
#   Right Arm   — upper arm + forearm + sword (blade + cross-guard)
#   Left Leg    — thigh + shin + boot
#   Right Leg   — thigh + shin + boot

